{"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusServer\/onNotifyFlags(flags:handler:)","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The notify signal is emitted on an object when one of its properties has"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"its value set through ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_set_property()"},{"text":", ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_set()"},{"type":"text","text":", et al."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"@discardableResult"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"onNotifyFlags","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"flags","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"ConnectFlags","preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject12ConnectFlagsV"},{"text":" = ConnectFlags(0), ","kind":"text"},{"text":"handler","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"@escaping"},{"kind":"text","text":" ("},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusServerRef","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"DBusServerRef","preciseIdentifier":"s:3GIO13DBusServerRefV"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject12ParamSpecRefV","text":"ParamSpecRef","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:s4Voida","text":"Void","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Int"}],"languages":["swift"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"parameters":[{"name":"flags","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Flags"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The signal handler to call"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"Run the given callback whenever the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":